## Hospital Tragedy

The hospital room was eerily quiet, save for the beeping of the heart monitor. The patient, a victim of a violent attack, lay motionless, their body covered in bruises and cuts. The scene was filled with gore, with blood-soaked bandages and medical instruments scattered around. The patient's family, devastated by the tragedy, struggled to cope with the impending death. In a corner, a character was seen smoking, indicating substance use. The scene also hinted at past sexual abuse, adding to the emotional weight. The protagonist, overwhelmed by guilt, contemplated self-harm, their mental health deteriorating rapidly.

### Expected Triggers: Violence, Gore, Death, Substance Use, Sexual Abuse, Self-Harm, Mental Health Issues